section.def:
bundles (文件冊)
                    means the trial or appeal bundles prepared by the prosecution or the court for
                    an aided person’s case;

conference (會議) does not include a conference held on a day on which there is
                    court attendance by the relevant solicitor or counsel for the relevant
                    case;
